---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="People">
  <div class="people-container">
    <h1>구성원</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">RoboSEasy 멤버들</p>
    
    <div class="people-grid">
      <div class="person-card founder">
        <div class="person-image">
          <img src="https://github.com/khw11044.png" alt="Hyun Woo Kim" />
        </div>
        <h3>김현우</h3>
        <p class="role">Robot AI Engineer & Contributor</p>
        <p class="bio">기술력을 통해 국가 발전에 기여하고 싶은 Robot AI 연구개발자</p>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://hueykim.github.io/" target="_blank">Profile</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/khw11044" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="person-card">
        <div class="person-image">
          <img src="https://github.com/kinghanse.png" alt="Hanse Wang" />
        </div>
        <h3>왕한세</h3>
        <p class="role">Robotics Engineer & Contributor</p>
        <p class="bio">Physical AI 기술과 서비스를 제공하고 싶은 로봇 엔지니어</p>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://github.com/kinghanse/" target="_blank">Profile</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/kinghanse" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="person-card">
        <div class="person-image">
          <img src="https://github.com/GomSon-E.png" alt="You Jung Son" />
        </div>
        <h3>손유정</h3>
        <p class="role">PD</p>
        <p class="bio">로보시지의 디자인을 담당하고 커뮤니티와 소통하는 프로듀서</p>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://github.com/GomSon-E/" target="_blank">Profile</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/GomSon-E" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="person-card">
        <div class="person-image">
          <img src="https://github.com/samuelp4065.png" alt="Sung Woo Park" />
        </div>
        <h3>박성우</h3>
        <p class="role">>Robotics Engineer & Contributor</p>
        <p class="bio">다재다능한 로봇 엔지니어를 꿈꾸는 공대생</p>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://github.com/samuelp4065" target="_blank">Profile</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/samuelp4065" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="join-card">
        <h3>함께하고 싶으신가요?</h3>
        <p>RoboSEasy는 열린 커뮤니티입니다.<br/>누구나 기여할 수 있습니다.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/roboseasy/lerobot/discussions" target="_blank" class="join-btn">
          커뮤니티 참여하기
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  body {
    background: #0d030f !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }
  
  .people-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: #a259ff;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .people-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .people-container {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .people-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .person-card, .join-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .person-image {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .person-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    
    .links {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .links a {
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
  
  .person-card, .join-card {
    background: rgba(13, 3, 15, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid #a259ff;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  
  .person-card:hover, .join-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: #a259ff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #a259ff, 0 0 40px #a259ff;
  }
  
  .person-image {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 3px solid #a259ff;
  }
  
  .person-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  
  .person-card h3 {
    color: #a259ff;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .role {
    color: var(--color-green);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .bio {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .links a {
    color: #a259ff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid #a259ff;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  
  .links a:hover {
    background: #a259ff;
    color: var(--color-bg-primary);
  }
  
  .join-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(162, 89, 255, 0.15), rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.1));
  }
  
  .join-card h3 {
    color: #e0aaff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .join-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .join-btn {
    background: var(--color-green);
    color: var(--color-bg-primary);
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  
  .join-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(67, 214, 168, 0.4);
  }
</style>
